room_info.description:
The elegant deluxe rooms at the hotel are the epitome of comfort and world class facilities. 
They have been aesthetically designed to meet the demands expected of star hotels. 
Each of these rooms is known for their ergonomic and voguish feature.
Having been designed with a large king size bedding facility, there is an added richness to the exorbitant space available.

Our deluxe suite rooms are in a class of its own. They are the right choice for the ubiquitous business travelers and holiday trevelers. 
The delight of our deluxe rooms will satisfy all the desired qualities of premium rooms. The contemporary ambience created with style and design 
showcases the exquisite room interiors in all its resplendence.

room_info.description: Premium Rooms feature king-size bed with mattresses, soft pillows and clean bed linens to ensure sound sleep to guests. Marble flooring, light colours on the walls with portraits and smart lamps make for graceful interiors. These rooms also have a working space with executive table and chair and upholsters to add to the convenience of guests.

Luxury rooms feature a queen-size bed that makes for a comfortable sleep for guests. The walls are painted in sober colours and attractive wallpapers, which gives an exquisite look to the room. The bathrooms are spacious and well-maintained with modern toiletries and complimentary shaving and tooth kits. Other in-room amenities include dressing mirror, tea/coffee maker, flat screen television and telephone.
